cytoscape.hyperedge
Interface SimMatcher

public interface SimMatcher

Interface used for matching similar HyperEdge objects. This is used in conjunction with the Matchable.isSimilar() operation.

Version:
1.0
Author:
Michael L. Creech
See Also:

similarTo

boolean similarTo(HyperEdge he1,
                  HyperEdge he2,
                  java.lang.Object optArgs)
Returns if two HyperEdge objects are similar.

Parameters:
he1 - the first HyperEdge to compare for similarity.
he2 - the second HyperEdge to compare for similarity.
optArgs - an object the may contain any optional information needed for computing the similarity.
Returns:
true if he1 is similar to he2. false otherwise.
